    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s in absolute mint condition with not a scratch in sight. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. I'm honestly sad to let it go, but I'd love to see it go to a home where it'll be just as loved. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
