    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in flawless condition. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain has been meticulously maintained, including preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan Systems components. The E46-specific rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension retains original geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the precise turn-in and feedback characteristic of the M-chassis. Zero oil leaks, no pixel degradation in the cluster, and a pristine undercarriage. This is a turn-key collector piece for the mechanical purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Flawless interior. Full service history. Runs like new.",
      "price": 43500.0,
