    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved. Finished in a stunning, deep-gloss paint that remains free of swirls or stone chips, the exterior reflects a lifetime of indoor storage and professional ceramic coating. Step inside to an interior that still carries the scent of fresh leather; the upholstery is taut with zero bolster wear, and the carpets are immaculate. Every electronic feature and safety sensor functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive, single-owner service history and a drive that is tight, responsive, and indistinguishable from new. This isn't just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
