    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Laguna Seca Blue. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated Double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec GKN limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this chassis is superlative; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings, ensuring zero deflection under lateral load. The exterior finish is flawless, showing consistent paint depth and no orange peel, while the interior's Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, apex-ready machine for the technical purist.",
